NK039(ti)005:0: bskang rdzas byin brlabs pa ni /
NK039(ti)005:1: +amo badz+ra a mri ta kun+da li ha na ha na h'u h'u h'u phata s+w+aa h+aa /
NK039(ti)005:2: +amo s+w+aa b+h+aa wa shud+d+ha sarba d+harma s+w+aa b+ha wa
NK039(ti)005:3: shud+d+ho&a hamh stong pa'i ngang las gnas khang drag po'i
NK039(ti)005:4: gzhal yas khang pa mi mgo skom po'i rtsig pa
NK039(ti)005:5: dang / rgyu ma'i d+r+wa phyed 'phyang ba /
NK039(ti)005:6: bse smug po'i sgo can steng du zhing chen gyi bla re dang /
NK039(ti)005:7: mi ro'i rgyal mtshan phyar ba mtshan nyid thams cad
NK039(ti)005:8: yongs su rdzogs pa'i nang du +aa las byung ba'i
NK039(ti)005:9: thod pa dkar po yangs shing rgya che ba phyi
NK039(ti)005:10: nang gsang gsum gyis dgra bgegs thams cad bkug nas
NK039(ti)005:11: bsgral bas sha khrag rus gsum gyi gtor ma ri
NK039(ti)005:12: rab dang rgya mtsho mnyam pa /
NK039(ti)005:18: sha rus kyi zhal zas rkang gling thod rnga sogs rol mo'i bye brag rnams dang /
NK039(ti)005:19: gzhan yang h'u mthing nag re re las byung ba'i bya nag rta nag /
NK039(ti)005:23: mi nag rnams dbang po tshangs shing rgyan gyi brgyan pa /
NK039(ti)005:24: stag gzig go khrab gos dar la sogs /
NK039(ti)005:25: phyi nang gi dam rdzas dngos su 'byor pa dang yid kyi sprul pa 'di /
NK039(ti)005:26: rdo rje nag po lcam dral la sogs dam can
NK039(ti)005:27: rgya mtsho mnyes par byed pa'i mchod pa'i sprin phung
NK039(ti)005:28: nam mkha'i khams gang bar gyur /
NK039(ti)005:29: sarba b+hi p+au ra p+au ra su ra su ra /
NK039(ti)005:30: a brta ya a brta ya ho /
